**Code Explanation:**

This script implements the full Step 4 training pipeline. It: 1. Loads training data and baselines, prepares normalized parameters and log-space residuals outside the training loop for efficiency. 2. Defines the CMBEmulatorModel (5-layer trunk, 1024 width, 256-unit heads) and CMBEmulator with float64 predict(). 3. Initializes fresh parameters (ignoring incompatible checkpoints). 4. Uses cosine annealing with warm restarts every 100 epochs via optax.join_schedules. 5. Trains for 500 epochs with batch size 512, evaluating cec.get_accuracy_score every 20 epochs and saving the best checkpoint based on mae_total. 6. After 500 epochs, if mae_total > 1e5, generates 50,000 extra samples and trains for 200 more epochs. 7. Saves best weights and metrics to disk. Units: TT/EE in K^2, PP dimensionless lensing potential, rho dimensionless correlation in [-1,1].

